Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.46,0:00:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿The VVV Project?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.76,0:00:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Given their stated position of peace through neutrality, ﻿JIOR can't possess a big military.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.89,0:00:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿And so, they developed weapons that could ﻿take on an entire fleet singlehandedly.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.31,0:00:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿So that's what ﻿the Valvraves are...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.23,0:00:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Still, I'm amazed that you managed to develop ﻿weapons that fit the bill so perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.90,0:00:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿It was because of ﻿the runes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.36,0:00:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿At the risk of oversimplifying, I suppose ﻿you could think of them as information particles.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.45,0:00:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿All physical matter is ﻿composed of atoms.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.00,0:00:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿In a similar vein, information is composed of ﻿indivisible units called runes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.13,0:00:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Or so ﻿they tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.84,0:00:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿"So they tell you"?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.02,0:00:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you ﻿a member of the development team?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.55,0:00:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Uh, right after I was assigned here, ﻿I butted heads with the top brass.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.30,0:00:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I was demoted to ﻿test subject caretaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.76,0:00:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Test subject... ﻿You mean the students?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.77,0:01:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Every last student at this school ﻿is being uniquely modified.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.15,0:01:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿That's why all the teachers were military.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.76,0:01:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿We're their caretakers.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.28,0:01:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Why is that woman ﻿the only exception?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.11,0:01:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Nanami-chan is ﻿a special case.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.03,0:01:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿We were set up to look like an ordinary school,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.70,0:01:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,so I guess ﻿they felt they had to stick in a PE student teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.20,0:01:19.71,Alt,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Stick in. Receive. Insert?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.33,0:01:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿It's a pretty weird ﻿program wizard, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.75,0:01:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Only VVVI ﻿has one.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.09,0:01:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Only VVVI can use ﻿that Harakiri Blade, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.89,0:01:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿This unit ﻿seems to be special.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.50,0:03:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Hey, nobody told me about ﻿this "Kamitsuki" stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.05,0:03:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿No, we didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.26,0:03:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Well, I knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.26,0:03:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Look, I know this might come as a shock, ﻿but try to stay calm, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.31,0:03:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Stay calm? This is ﻿totally bad-ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.94,0:03:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿This is your usual "immortal anti-hero" deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.25,0:03:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Do we have a special pose or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.32,0:03:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Thank goodness ﻿he's so stupid...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.61,0:03:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Say what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.40,0:03:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Now, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.32,0:03:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Let's all try to get along. ﻿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.60,0:03:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We're gonna be a team from now on, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.07,0:03:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿A team...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.53,0:03:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿In other words, ﻿none of us is alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.54,0:03:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.16,0:03:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}﻿So much for ﻿being alone together...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.50,0:03:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}﻿Not at all, it would appear that ﻿my staff treated you quite rudely.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.21,0:03:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}﻿I'll apologize again ﻿once the ceremony is over.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.91,0:03:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Ceremony?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.92,0:03:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}﻿You and your students are heroes. ﻿{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.44,0:04:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Of course there will be a ceremony.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.93,0:04:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}﻿Between the international congress and media interviews, ﻿things are about to become quite hectic.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.31,0:04:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}﻿I must be going. Let's meet on the Moon, ﻿Representative Rion Nanami.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.07,0:04:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I can't... I can't ﻿keep doing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.15,0:04:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I'm sorry I'm all dirty! Miyamoto said ﻿his favorite model had been buried.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.49,0:04:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}﻿Found it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.45,0:04:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I can relate... I couldn't bear it ﻿if my favorite shirt got buried!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.17,0:04:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.88,0:04:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Go on, try it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.05,0:04:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I know, aren't they great?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.73,0:04:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I totally recommend these! ﻿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.36,0:04:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Potato chips dipped in red chile oil!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.93,0:04:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Hey, once we get to the Moon, ﻿come shopping with me at the supermarket!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.69,0:04:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I know these!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.11,0:04:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿You like ﻿these wafers?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.28,0:05:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿The fukujinzuke relish coating ﻿on these is so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.11,0:05:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿And if you fry them, it takes them ﻿to a whole new level!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.91,0:05:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿The trick is ﻿to use olive oil!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.37,0:05:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿What do you say, ﻿Akira-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.09,0:05:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Experiment?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.30,0:05:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. It's in our best interest to learn more about ﻿what our bodies can do, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.97,0:05:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿You have a point.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.64,0:05:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Let's start with jumping jacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.82,0:05:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Duration and number. And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.14,0:05:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.90,0:05:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.23,0:05:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I'm saying that ﻿we should test it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.32,0:05:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿What are you ﻿talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.94,0:05:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿What? Hey! ﻿Say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.41,0:05:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿C'mon, man up! ﻿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.28,0:05:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You're ignoring me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.32,0:05:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿We all know ﻿you like her!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.24,0:05:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Right? Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.07,0:05:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.04,0:05:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Let me show you ﻿my special stash!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.21,0:05:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿It's enormous...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.25,0:05:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿You can use ﻿a ruler for that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.38,0:05:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I know, right? ﻿This'll do the trick for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.34,0:06:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}﻿Everyone, this is student ﻿teacher Rion Nanami.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.76,0:06:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}﻿We will be arriving at the Moon soon.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.00,0:06:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿{\i1}﻿Oops, I didn't mean to rhyme!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.35,0:06:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿When we arrive, we will need a representative
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.70,0:06:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,for various ﻿international negotiations and interviews and things.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.61,0:06:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}﻿Up until now, I've done what I can ﻿to fill that role, but I don't think it's right.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.78,0:06:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}﻿It shouldn't be because someone is ﻿older or a teacher or whatever.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.99,0:06:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿And so, I think we should hold an election!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.66,0:06:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿An election for the Prime Minister of JIOR!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.41,0:06:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿An election?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.62,0:06:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿We're gonna be ﻿the country’s leaders?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.46,0:06:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿That's a great idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.54,0:06:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I want to ﻿try it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.54,0:06:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿We have the 7th off, ﻿let's do it then!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.46,0:06:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿We're technically "﻿off" now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.88,0:06:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿That sounds like fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.21,0:06:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿It sure does!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.51,0:06:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Prime Minister...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.05,0:06:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿As you can see, our food self-sufficiency ﻿has been improved to 17%.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.10,0:06:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And this isn't the only benefit to come from the Seven R's.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.81,0:06:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Senpai, who will you ﻿vote for?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.11,0:07:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Isn't it obvious? ﻿For the winning candidate.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.44,0:07:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Our public relations activities via the wired ﻿are also going all-out now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.82,0:07:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,To give an example—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.04,0:07:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I'm running for election, too! ﻿Thank you for your support!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.50,0:07:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿So you were ﻿serious, Yamada...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.88,0:07:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿How many times do I have to ﻿tell you it's "Thunder"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.80,0:07:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿To keep our secret, it would be best ﻿if one of us was in a leadership position.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.93,0:07:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿You run, Haruto.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.39,0:07:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I can't! I just don't ﻿have it in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.64,0:07:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Yeah, somebody crazy like Shoko ﻿would be a better fit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.89,0:07:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿If it's "crazy" that matters, ﻿he might actually be a good choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.65,0:07:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Say what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.94,0:07:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿It's a compliment! She's saying ﻿that you're more of a leader than I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.28,0:07:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Oh, she is? ﻿I suppose I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.16,0:07:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿You're a real ﻿sweetheart, ain'tcha?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.24,0:07:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.50,0:08:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I'm surprised. I didn't expect you ﻿to volunteer to act as election supervisor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.59,0:08:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I'm a refugee, ﻿so I don't have voting rights.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.91,0:08:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I assume you aren't trying to ﻿pull a fast one on us again?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.81,0:08:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿The election of a representative ﻿aligns with my own objectives.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.64,0:08:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿It will be ﻿a fair election.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.56,0:08:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I thought you wanted to quit ﻿being our representative.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.86,0:08:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I don't want to run away from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.66,0:08:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'm going to ﻿represent everyone,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.62,0:08:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to be properly chosen to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.70,0:08:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.86,0:08:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿You would've made ﻿one hell of a teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.24,0:08:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Don't treat me ﻿like a child!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.58,0:08:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Sorry, my bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.58,0:08:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿He wasn't elected student council president ﻿three years in a row for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.10,0:08:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}﻿Trapped in ﻿a room together...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.94,0:09:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}﻿I'll keep you ﻿girls safe.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.15,0:09:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}﻿Also, your mouth... There's too many ﻿words coming out of it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.78,0:09:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Takahi-senpai, I—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.87,0:09:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Get over ﻿yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.20,0:09:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I don't care how famous you are or ﻿that you're a pilot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.90,0:09:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just an underclassman to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.62,0:09:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Before this war broke out, ﻿I didn't even know your name!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.67,0:09:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I'm not as—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.26,0:09:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿What's wrong, ﻿Tokishma?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.55,0:09:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Takahi-senpai, ﻿stand back...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.69,0:09:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Miss Rukino?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.06,0:09:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿You go after everything, ﻿don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.19,0:09:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Haru-tard, you can't jump her ﻿just because she's got a sexy body.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.62,0:09:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Oh. Um, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.95,0:10:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿She's right! You're so sexy—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.89,0:10:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I mean lovely, that I couldn't help myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.92,0:10:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Dressed like that, you're asking for ﻿all kinds of unwanted attention from the boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.05,0:10:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I'm really sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.55,0:10:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Wait a minute! ﻿Come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.76,0:10:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿The interval between ﻿attacks is shortening?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.68,0:10:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I'm scared. What if it keeps getting ﻿shorter and eventually reaches zero?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.68,0:10:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I'm worried that I'll run around ﻿attacking people like some kind of animal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.44,0:10:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Haruto.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.90,0:10:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿If that ever happens, ﻿I'll put you down.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.28,0:10:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿If I'm going to be killed by someone, ﻿I'd like it to be you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.83,0:10:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Shoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.42,0:10:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Miss Rukino... Um, ﻿are you guys training?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.92,0:10:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿No, we just bumped into ﻿each other, and—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.17,0:10:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿You're not ﻿running?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.67,0:10:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿The election.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.22,0:10:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿No, no! I'm not ﻿cut out for that stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.22,0:11:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿It should be ﻿a third-year who—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.27,0:11:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.27,0:11:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿The members of the Youth Culture Club ﻿decided to vote for you, Shoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.52,0:11:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿You saved my ﻿Shadow X, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.69,0:11:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿And I hear you went to the student council president ﻿and renegotiated the Light Music Club's budget!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.24,0:11:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I only did that ﻿because I'm a fan of theirs.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.53,0:11:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿What's this? Are you gonna ﻿run in the election, Shoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.99,0:11:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿No, no way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.91,0:11:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿You'd do a great job! ﻿I know it! You've got to run!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.04,0:11:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿But I'm just not—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.54,0:11:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿You've always been there ﻿at our matches, cheering us on!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.00,0:11:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿And you've always brought us food, too! ﻿I honestly think you can do it, Shoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.17,0:11:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Cut it out, ﻿I'm not like that at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.88,0:11:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿You're giving me ﻿too much credit, really!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.88,0:11:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Oh, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.00,0:11:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.88,0:11:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I can't, I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.85,0:11:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿If they can reach the neutral territory of the Moon, ﻿we'll no longer be able to move against them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.60,0:11:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿This next battle ﻿will likely be the last.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.81,0:11:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿We won't let them ﻿escape, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.15,0:11:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿We swear on the honor ﻿of the Karlstein Agency.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.90,0:11:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I'll be joining you ﻿this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.03,0:11:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿If the Valvraves slip through my grasp, ﻿it might cost me my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.74,0:11:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Never! 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.34,0:12:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible, you are the Chancellor's close friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.70,0:12:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿That wasn't the case 20 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.09,0:12:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿And he wasn't the Chancellor then, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.96,0:12:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Are you concerned about ﻿the royalists staging a comeback, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.09,0:12:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿That is part of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.71,0:12:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Where is ﻿H-neun?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.21,0:12:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Playing hooky, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.68,0:12:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿My dear!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.31,0:12:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿You and me, we're like ﻿peas in a pod!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.31,0:12:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Us running into each other here, ﻿don't you feel the hand of fate at work?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.98,0:12:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿What are you ﻿doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.78,0:12:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿That's a long ﻿story...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.11,0:12:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿For now, ﻿how about some tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.49,0:12:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Where's Shoko? ﻿Isn't she with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.57,0:12:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿She said she would ﻿catch up with us later.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.36,0:12:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Why do you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.62,0:12:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿She just seemed like ﻿she wasn't her usual self.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.95,0:13:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿You think?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.98,0:13:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿She didn't look ﻿all that different to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.08,0:13:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Well, ﻿she was just—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.04,0:13:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Haruto.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.29,0:13:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Can I trust you ﻿to look out for Shoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.09,0:13:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I'll come right out ﻿and ask her what's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.22,0:13:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I'll leave her ﻿to you, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.39,0:13:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I'll go ﻿look for her!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.35,0:13:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Don't be late!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.60,0:13:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.32,0:13:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Shoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.11,0:13:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}﻿So does this mean that Prime Minister ﻿Sashinami has been killed?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.91,0:13:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}﻿Take a look at the signature on ﻿the declaration of unconditional surrender.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.21,0:13:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}﻿It says "Acting Prime Minister ﻿"Yamamoto," see?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.11,0:13:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}﻿It's possible that he fled, ﻿but in all likelihood...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.05,0:13:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Shoko... What was ﻿that just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.09,0:14:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿He's alive. ﻿He's alive, I know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.14,0:14:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Why do we have to pick ﻿a new prime minister?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.39,0:14:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Don't bury my dad in the past... ﻿Don't assume he's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.23,0:14:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Shoko... How long ﻿have you known?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.07,0:14:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿No way... ﻿Since way back then?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.83,0:14:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}﻿But that would mean ﻿this whole time,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.50,0:14:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}﻿she's been carrying ﻿this all alone.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.48,0:14:48.98,Alt,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"May my dad be safe."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.69,0:14:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}﻿I'm such an idiot!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.48,0:14:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}﻿Why didn't I ﻿see it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.74,0:15:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}﻿All this time, Shoko's been fighting ﻿by herself! Fighting all alone!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.33,0:15:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Just you wait, Shoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.17,0:15:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll bring ﻿your father back with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.13,0:15:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.14,0:15:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I'm not around, ﻿Miss Rukino is here. L-elf, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.26,0:15:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Haruto, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.80,0:15:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿It's crazy! ﻿You can't do it alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.43,0:15:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I know it's crazy, ﻿but I'm going anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.97,0:15:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿You don't know what you're saying!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.31,0:15:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿If you did, you wouldn't go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.47,0:15:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿No, I'm going.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.72,0:15:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿He's not your father, Haruto, ﻿he's mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.00,0:15:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's none of your concern!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.48,0:15:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Of course it is! ﻿Because you're crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.02,0:15:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Someone who's precious to me is crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.09,0:15:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿If this isn't a time to do something crazy, what is?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.53,0:15:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Someone precious... ﻿to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.45,0:15:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Oh, um, ﻿I just meant...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.08,0:15:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Basically, I'm ready to go that far for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.59,0:15:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I mean, we've known each other forever...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.88,0:15:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.63,0:16:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Thank you, ﻿Haruto.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.22,0:16:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I'll run ﻿in the election.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.30,0:16:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I want to fight ﻿alongside you, too, Haruto.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.06,0:16:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I want to stand shoulder to shoulder with you, ﻿not just be protected all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.85,0:16:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Shoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.06,0:16:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Besides, if we're going to save anyone, ﻿it should be all our families.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.78,0:16:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.74,0:16:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿It's time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.70,0:16:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.04,0:16:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I'm running ﻿in the election, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.00,0:16:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I figured ﻿you'd come.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.17,0:16:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.30,0:16:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Your application. I already filled in ﻿all the required fields.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.76,0:16:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Thanks, Marie!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.85,0:16:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Haruto.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.31,0:16:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I want to straighten this up ﻿before heading back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.27,0:16:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿It won't work out, not between ﻿a Kamitsuki and a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.19,0:17:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Maybe you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.19,0:17:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Are you an idiot? A "like" without ﻿getting something back isn't a "like" that'll last.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.61,0:17:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Even so, ﻿I'm going to—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.91,0:17:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Haruto?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.58,0:17:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.09,0:17:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿In closing, I pledge to you a better food situation, a steady ﻿supply of power,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.79,0:17:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,and a stable lifestyle with these Seven R's.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.14,0:17:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,He's as persuasive ﻿as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.13,0:17:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿He is the student council ﻿president, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.60,0:17:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿He makes you ﻿want to vote for him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.73,0:17:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Next is our final candidate. ﻿Shoko Sashinami of Year 2 Class B.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.99,0:17:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Nobody likes it when somebody ﻿wins without a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.06,0:17:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Oh, she decided to run after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.22,0:17:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoko, you can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.08,0:17:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Guys! When we get to the Moon,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.79,0:17:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿let's hold the school festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.25,0:17:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿The school festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.04,0:17:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿W-What's ﻿she saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.09,0:18:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Hold the school festival?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.09,0:18:03.96,Alt,,0,0,0,,﻿I'd go for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.96,0:18:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Come on, ﻿take this seriously!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.47,0:18:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿It was called off ﻿because of the war, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.72,0:18:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I'm so psyched about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.80,0:18:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, ﻿last year's was awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.73,0:18:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Right, Otamaya?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.02,0:18:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.11,0:18:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿You showed me the monster suit ﻿for that movie you were making, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.28,0:18:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I've been looking forward to ﻿seeing it at the school festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.24,0:18:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Yeah, that movie's ﻿our pride and joy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.00,0:18:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I thought ﻿as much!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.99,0:18:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Takano-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.17,0:18:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We all swooned over ﻿your Romeo last year!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.79,0:18:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿This year, we're doing The Cherry Orchard!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.06,0:18:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿But with all the genders reversed!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.21,0:18:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿That I've got to see!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.50,0:18:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Shoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.59,0:18:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Come hear our ﻿performance, too, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.84,0:18:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿We were able to get our ﻿instruments fixed, thanks to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.72,0:18:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Will do! ﻿I'll see it for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.01,0:18:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Come eat at ﻿our booth, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.64,0:18:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I'm looking forward to ﻿your Machida Special!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.43,0:18:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Our exhibit's gonna be ﻿awesome, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.31,0:18:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I want to make ours ﻿a coffee shop!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.06,0:19:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿It'll be revenge ﻿for last year!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.06,0:19:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿The zero-G ballet ﻿was amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.02,0:19:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Sashinami, we're fighting a war!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.45,0:19:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have ﻿the luxury of throwing a school festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.95,0:19:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿That's why ﻿we have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.07,0:19:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿He's right, we're in ﻿the middle of a war.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.83,0:19:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿There's no telling ﻿when we might die.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.00,0:19:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿That's exactly why I want to ﻿hold the school festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.25,0:19:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿This might be the only chance ﻿we'll ever get to be students!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.38,0:19:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Club activities, field trips, field days, ﻿there's a ton of things that I want to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.05,0:19:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I don't want to give up ﻿a single one of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.04,0:19:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿What do you say, everyone? ﻿Let's be more selfish!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.77,0:19:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I know that it'll give us a reason ﻿to go on fighting! It'll get us amped up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.98,0:19:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I have a reason ﻿to go on fighting, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.98,0:19:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿When we get to the Moon...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.14,0:19:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Um, this is just me, mind you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.86,0:19:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Um, how can I ﻿put it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.78,0:19:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I... I'm gonna tell the person ﻿I like exactly how I feel!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.79,0:20:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I have a reason ﻿to keep going, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.88,0:20:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Do you think ﻿she means me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.59,0:20:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿No way! ﻿She means me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.42,0:20:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Hey, are you ﻿okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.76,0:20:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Are you having trouble breathing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.20,0:20:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Go ahead and body-jack me. I feel fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.02,0:20:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I have one, too! To be ﻿the richest man in the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.22,0:20:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿To compete in ﻿the inter-high tournament!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.82,0:20:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿To make my ﻿pro debut!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.19,0:20:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿To become ﻿even stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.45,0:20:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿To buy as many ﻿GX3000's as I can!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.36,0:20:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I-I'll profess ﻿my feelings, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.37,0:20:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿To become a novelist!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.37,0:20:39.08,Alt,,0,0,0,,To make 100 friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.08,0:20:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Guys, let's do everything that we've always dreamed of! ﻿Let's become the kings of selfishness!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.97,0:20:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Hey! W-What are ﻿you thinking—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.39,0:20:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿We only go around ﻿once in life!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.48,0:20:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿The things we want to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.95,0:20:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The dreams ﻿we want to fulfill!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.64,0:20:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's try to do them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.82,0:21:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.73,0:21:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you only get one life!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.57,0:21:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Let's be selfish!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.66,0:21:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿This can't be ﻿happening...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.37,0:21:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}﻿Is this—{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.92,0:21:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿When we get to the Moon, ﻿let's all do whatever we want!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.59,0:21:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Let's find something different! ﻿Something new!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.35,0:21:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}﻿Now I get it...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.64,0:21:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}﻿This really is ﻿a curse, isn't it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.82,0:21:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I know we're gonna be okay! ﻿I know we can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.46,0:22:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}﻿Tell me ﻿Haruto...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.01,0:22:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}﻿Do you think ﻿I did okay?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.66,0:22:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿This says ﻿that Shoko won.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.26,0:24:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Next time, episode 11, ﻿Military Tribunal #54".
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.98,0:24:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Valvrave the Liberator...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.68,0:24:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The system that will ﻿expose the truth of the world.
